  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced", 
    "date": "1981-01-05", 
    "text": "Neighborhood School Act - Eliminates the jurisdiction of Federal courts to make any decision, enter any judgment, or issue any order with regard to the assignment of pupils to a particular school on the basis of their race, color, religion, or national origin. Prohibits the withholding of Federal financial assistance to achieve such student assignment."
